rounded up a test group,

00:06:26.400 --> 00:06:28.730 align:middle line:84%
I believe somewhere in
the couple of thousands,

00:06:28.730 --> 00:06:31.220 align:middle line:84%
3,000 maybe, and
changed their diets out.

00:06:31.220 --> 00:06:33.720 align:middle line:84%
And changed their diets out,
gave them some supplementation,

00:06:33.720 --> 00:06:34.848 align:middle line:90%
changed their diets out.

00:06:34.848 --> 00:06:36.390 align:middle line:84%
In other words, what
he wanted to see

00:06:36.390 --> 00:06:38.295 align:middle line:84%
was, and these were the
criminals beating up

00:06:38.295 --> 00:06:40.170 align:middle line:84%
other criminals, these
were the violent ones.

00:06:40.170 --> 00:06:42.003 align:middle line:84%
What he wanted to find
out was whether there

00:06:42.003 --> 00:06:46.230 align:middle line:84%
